over the years. We especially welcome the feedback we've gotten, which has 
given us insight into the potential benefits of our formulations.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="sqsrte-large">We are grateful to all the loyal customers who have purchased our products over the years. We especially welcome the feedback we've gotten, which has given us insight into the potential benefits of our formulations. As we've concluded challenge studies, we have found our home in our new brand, Florent. Pronounced "flora" in French, Florent denotes the biome, the ecosystem of probiotics that live on the surface of our skin. As we move forward, we will be conducting further testing of our products to demonstrate their efficacy in preserving the skin biome. We are confident that this new line of products are the most stable and sophisticated we have yet produced. </p>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
